0x8ab718c34fadcda7 expref: 749228 pid: 53633 timeout: 83037 lvb_type: 0
Jun 11 23:27:52 ai400x2t-01-vm00 kernel: LustreError: 2553724:0:(ldlm_lockd.c:2521:ldlm_cancel_handler()) ldlm_cancel from 172.16.2.247@tcp arrived at 1718148472 with bad export cookie 5851826019857969025
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;we probably need dlmtrace logs from clients to better understand that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
